Title: Dew Drop Serum — UGC Reel
Author: wavelet-director

INT. BATHROOM VANITY - DAY

DANA, late twenties, sits at her bright bathroom vanity in a cream tank top. Soft daylight from a frosted window camera-left. She looks straight into the lens like she's texting a friend a recommendation. Medium close-up, chest-up.

DANA
Okay this serum has actually changed my skin. I'm three weeks in and my whole vibe is just... glowy now.

CUT TO:

INT. BATHROOM COUNTER - DAY (ECU)

Extreme close-up: Dana's hands hold a small frosted-glass dropper bottle over her open palm. She squeezes one bead of clear serum onto her fingertip. Cream marble counter softly out of focus behind. Same warm daylight from camera-left.

DANA (V.O.)
One drop. That's it. The whole bottle lasted me a month.

CUT TO:

INT. LIVING ROOM WINDOW - DAY

Dana stands by a tall window, soft late-morning daylight wrapping camera-left. Same cream tank top. She tucks her hair behind her ear, half-smiles into the lens. Medium close-up, chest-up.

DANA
Hyaluronic acid plus niacinamide. Genuinely. Just try it.

FADE OUT.
